summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 4469 for the improvement of Heights Avenue, from 41st Avenue Southwest to 42nd Avenue Southwest, and certain parts of certain other streets and avenues, by grading and otherwise improving the same; under Ordinance No. 52637, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
